extends baseEmail

block content
  p Hello #{donorName},
  p Your project brief is now active! Execution has begun on your approved project.
  p
    strong Project Details:
  ul
    li
      strong Title: 
      | #{projectTitle}
    li
      strong Description: 
      | #{projectDescription}
    li
      strong Budget: 
      | #{budget} NGN
    li
      strong Location: 
      | #{state}, #{city}
  p An NGO has been selected to execute this project. You can monitor the project progress and receive milestone updates directly from your dashboard.
  p Exciting times ahead! Your donation is now making a real difference.
  p For any updates or inquiries regarding your project, please visit your dashboard or contact our support team.
  p Thank you for your continued support in creating positive change!
